flowchart LR
  Analyst[Analyst / Supervisor / Auditor] --> UI[React FraudOps Console]
  UI -->|REST + bearer/API key| API[FastAPI Fraud API]
  Generator[Transaction Generator] -->|validated transaction schema| Kafka[(Kafka)]
  API -->|validated transaction schema| Kafka

  Kafka --> Consumer[Stream Consumer]
  Consumer --> Redis[(Redis Feature Windows)]
  Consumer --> Neo4j[(Neo4j Entity Graph)]
  Consumer --> Postgres[(PostgreSQL Transactions / Alerts / Audit)]
  Consumer --> DLQ[(Dead Letter Queue)]

  Redis --> Features[Feature Engineering]
  Neo4j --> GraphFeatures[Graph Features]
  Features --> Ensemble[ML Ensemble Scoring]
  GraphFeatures --> Ensemble
  MinIO[(MinIO Model Artifacts)] --> Ensemble
  Ensemble --> Explain[SHAP-style Explanations]
  Explain --> Narrative[LLM / Local Narrative]

  API --> Postgres
  API --> Compliance[Compliance Services]
  Compliance --> Watchlists[OFAC / UNSC / EU / SEBI Watchlists]
  Compliance --> Reports[SAR / STR Drafts]
  Compliance --> Audit[Hash-linked Audit Evidence]

  API --> Governance[Model Governance API]
  Governance --> Postgres
  Governance --> MinIO

  Postgres --> UI
  Neo4j --> UI
  Reports --> UI
  DLQ --> UI
  Governance --> UI

  API --> Prometheus[Prometheus Metrics]
  Prometheus --> Grafana[Grafana Dashboards]
  API --> Logstash[Logstash]
  Logstash --> Elastic[(Elasticsearch)]
  Elastic --> Kibana[Kibana Logs]
